interpretation: The "custard" card represents indulgence and satisfaction. It signifies a time of contentment, pleasure, and abundance. You may be feeling a sense of ease and comfort in your life, enjoying the fruits of your labor. However, be cautious not to become too complacent and take things for granted. Too much indulgence can lead to stagnation and complacency. This card also encourages you to savor the moment and appreciate the simple pleasures in life. Embrace the sweetness of life and allow yourself to experience joy.
